results.name: First row of infinite Sudoku-type array A269526.
comment: Conjectured to be a permutation of the natural numbers.
It would be nice to have a formula or recurrence.  Note that the first row of the analogous array corresponding to the Wythoff game, A004482, does have a simple formula.
See A295563 for much more about this sequence. - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Mar 10 2019
